{"word":"πουλυβότειρα","slug":"πουλυβότειρα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n86094\" key=\"poulubo/teira\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">πουλῠβότειρα</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, metri gr. for <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">πολυβότειρα,</foreign> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author> </bibl> and <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hes.\">Hes.</a></author> </bibl>; so all other compds. with <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">πολύ</foreign> may be lengthd. in hexameter verse to <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">πουλυ-,</foreign> metri gr., <sense id=\"n86094.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">v.</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">πολυ-</ref> </xr>:—<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author> </bibl> however uses the licence only in this word, in the gen. sg. of <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">πουλύπους,</foreign> and in the pr. n. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Πουλυδάμας.</foreign> </sense> </entryFree>"}]}